---
title: Rosti-Topped Lentil Pie with Garlicky Green Beans
description: Massaman curry paste is a type of Thai red curry that is packed full of flavour. This lentil pie is a take on a classic shepherd's pie. You won't miss the meat or the mashed potato in this dish as it's packed full of flavour and topped with crispy potato.
